{"tid":2404689,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"[DC] 打機吹水谷","createTime":"2021-02-12T01:10:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-23T06:02:35.000Z","uid":145108,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f7e0c43f0e0bcba9853e7ca5a11a05e1f92720c0","tid":2404689,"uid":145108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T01:10:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果有興趣 歡迎入坑DC：<br />\n<a href=\"https://discord.gg/5Nkga6j\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdiscord.gg%2F5Nkga6j&d=fMmZVRBh8JxXvfCabRklGVQmTevdAkBFS5MHro4yyYg%3D&h=90120d34\" target=\"_blank\">https://discord.gg/5Nkga6j</a><br />\n<br />\n大家好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我地主要係放工後先上線，平時主要係扮工吹水Group<br />\n希望大家熱情d 講多d野 唔洗怕羞 唔好咩都唔講 hi下都好<br />\n仲有想大家多D入DISCORD 咁先會容易搵到人打機 <br />\n就算唔打機 吹下水都可以好開心<br />\n會玩既遊戲有好多種類 Steam Game PC PS4 Switch<br />\n我地依家會主力Steam Game<br />\n多數係合作類 我地有位熱心既巴打整左個List<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋我地依家用埋Parsec，<br />\n可以一齊玩一定單機多人(例如Overcooked)既遊戲，<br />\n亦會係扮工時間玩Telegram既遊戲，<br />\n例如狼人、Spyfall、牛頭王、Dixit、犯人在跳舞、Avalon，<br />\n大家如果有興趣既 歡迎隨時加入我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一部份我地集體玩過既Game：<br />\n<br />\nLOL 唔使多講 我地會打內戰 NG RANK 捉棋<br />\n但主要係玩得開心 如果太認真會失去左個樂趣 <br />\n笑下玩下鳩野 比羸更加重要<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nCastle Crashers<br />\n是一款2D橫向卷軸動作冒險RPG，角色豐富、劇情精彩、遊戲要素多元，是一款非常適合多人連線的休閒遊戲！<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bu6Kwvd695w&amp;ab_channel=TheBehemoth\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dbu6Kwvd695w%26ab_channel%3DTheBehemoth&d=fMmZVRBh8JxXvfCabRklGVQmTevdAkBFS5MHro4yyYg%3D&h=1682c6ef\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bu6Kwvd695w&amp;ab_channel=TheBehemoth</a><br />\n<br />\nSecrets of grindea<br />\n《格蘭蒂亞秘聞（Secrets of Grindea）》是瑞典知名獨立遊戲工作室瑞典知名Pixel Ferrets，基於中世紀本土的歷史所創造的一款RPG遊戲,經歷多年 但依然有更新 絕對值得一玩。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xDCLz_coPHs&amp;ab_channel=SecretsOfGrindea\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DxDCLz_coPHs%26ab_channel%3DSecretsOfGrindea&d=fMmZVRBh8JxXvfCabRklGVQmTevdAkBFS5MHro4yyYg%3D&h=55c266ca\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xDCLz_coPHs&amp;ab_channel=SecretsOfGrindea</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nDivinity original sin 2 <br />\n由Larian Studios開發的RPG遊戲《神諭 原罪》推出了最新續作&mdash;&mdash;《神諭 原罪2》，這部作品獲得了諸多媒體的高分評價，其中IGN就給出了9.6的高分。並且這部新作是基於《神諭 原罪》和《神諭 原罪加強版》開發的，相信《神諭 原罪2》會成為一部真・神作。《神諭 原罪2》是一款具備單人和多人模式，以團隊配合為基礎的角色扮演遊戲，這部作品的故事背景設定在前作故事的數個世代之後，相較於前作出身和種族等關係將近一步深化，遊戲將包含更大的發掘要素。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vJ4SVSm1ARQ&amp;ab_channel=PlayStation\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DvJ4SVSm1ARQ%26ab_channel%3DPlayStation&d=fMmZVRBh8JxXvfCabRklGVQmTevdAkBFS5MHro4yyYg%3D&h=4a8cd03e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vJ4SVSm1ARQ&amp;ab_channel=PlayStation</a><br />\n<br />\nPuyo Puyo Tetris<br />\n由小妹帶你重新認識俄羅斯方塊<br />\n<a href=\"https://store.steampowered.com/app/546050/Puyo_PuyoTetris/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstore.steampowered.com%2Fapp%2F546050%2FPuyo_PuyoTetris%2F&d=fMmZVRBh8JxXvfCabRklGVQmTevdAkBFS5MHro4yyYg%3D&h=eb855bda\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://store.steampowered.com/app/546050/Puyo_PuyoTetris/</a><br />\n<br />\nRaft  <br />\n一隻海上生存遊戲，要靠海上既漂浮物去獲取資源，或許去海底自己搵，<br />\n但係海上有好多鯊魚會攻擊你，慢慢研發科技進行反擊<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KTutxuWCnBI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DKTutxuWCnBI&d=fMmZVRBh8JxXvfCabRklGVQmTevdAkBFS5MHro4yyYg%3D&h=fe546ebc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KTutxuWCnBI</a><br />\n<br />\nTower Unite 好鬼多人<br />\n原身係GMOD 入邊既一個大MOD，後來自己出左隻GAME，<br />\n依隻GAME既特色係大集合，可以好多人一齊玩一啲小遊戲，<br />\n例如打MINI GOLF、MONKEY BALL、或許鬼捉人之類，<br />\n除左本身既遊戲 佢既社區入邊都仲有好多小玩意，<br />\n例如 打保齡球、去賭場賭錢、跑馬之類 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NFnUCqkHnqc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DNFnUCqkHnqc&d=fMmZVRBh8JxXvfCabRklGVQmTevdAkBFS5MHro4yyYg%3D&h=001c7934\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NFnUCqkHnqc</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NUZnTCt7D8M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DNUZnTCt7D8M&d=fMmZVRBh8JxXvfCabRklGVQmTevdAkBFS5MHro4yyYg%3D&h=6b0945b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NUZnTCt7D8M</a><br />\n <br />\nBLOONS TD6<br />\n最多四人既塔防守城 玩法有趣 中意玩WAR3 TD既朋友啱晒<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PvFaD6g6yzk&amp;ab_channel=TapTapPlay\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DPvFaD6g6yzk%26ab_channel%3DTapTapPlay&d=fMmZVRBh8JxXvfCabRklGVQmTevdAkBFS5MHro4yyYg%3D&h=cd9ac0ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PvFaD6g6yzk&amp;ab_channel=TapTapPlay</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nTricky Tower 四人 [單機多人]<br />\n一隻類似俄羅斯方塊既GAME，佢有三個模式，<br />\n有好多道具去增加幫自己或者破壞對手既塔，<br />\n例如 唔比轉方向、將D方塊變到好大舊，<br />\n係一隻唔錯既小品<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0Q6lgXjdJiE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D0Q6lgXjdJiE&d=fMmZVRBh8JxXvfCabRklGVQmTevdAkBFS5MHro4yyYg%3D&h=836f3568\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0Q6lgXjdJiE</a><br />\n<br />\nUltimate Chicken Horse (超級雞馬) 四人 [單機多人]<br />\n畫風偏可愛，搞笑小品，<br />\n佢最大特色係害人害己，每一個回合可以放一件物品去增加過關既難度，<br />\n目的就係要害死人既同時，自己又過到關，<br />\n放工玩下輕鬆下係唔錯既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Biijaxbtsks\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DBiijaxbtsks&d=fMmZVRBh8JxXvfCabRklGVQmTevdAkBFS5MHro4yyYg%3D&h=a75dd87b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Biijaxbtsks</a><br />\n<br />\nHuman: Fall Flat 八人<br />\n一隻合作過關既遊戲 畫風好有趣 D人好似泥膠<br />\n玩落會好有喜感 不自覺咁覺得好好笑 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/p0MxFn5.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fp0MxFn5.jpg&d=fMmZVRBh8JxXvfCabRklGVQmTevdAkBFS5MHro4yyYg%3D&h=04613076\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://i.imgur.com/p0MxFn5.jpg</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/XEZiRmW.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FXEZiRmW.jpg&d=fMmZVRBh8JxXvfCabRklGVQmTevdAkBFS5MHro4yyYg%3D&h=11f63df1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://i.imgur.com/XEZiRmW.jpg</a><br />\n玩到拍埋片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/iPNVCSGuu9s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FiPNVCSGuu9s&d=fMmZVRBh8JxXvfCabRklGVQmTevdAkBFS5MHro4yyYg%3D&h=0068bd45\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/iPNVCSGuu9s</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/sidFqyKcG4Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FsidFqyKcG4Q&d=fMmZVRBh8JxXvfCabRklGVQmTevdAkBFS5MHro4yyYg%3D&h=a1a5e433\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/sidFqyKcG4Q</a><br />\n<br />\nHeroes of Hammerwatch 好鬼多人<br />\n遊戲目標基本上就係一直前進，打低最後既BOSS，<br />\n每一關都有四層，第四層就係BOSS戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n遊戲過程會拎到一啲裝備，但Gameover之後，依啲裝備會無晒，但人物lv會keep住。<br />\n如果你中途死左既話，救你既人既靈魂就會同你連埋，<br />\n其中一個人死既話，其他連結左既人就會一齊死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以最後一個人死，就會全部人一次過死晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/8xqbB0Q.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F8xqbB0Q.jpg&d=fMmZVRBh8JxXvfCabRklGVQmTevdAkBFS5MHro4yyYg%3D&h=a811ef65\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://i.imgur.com/8xqbB0Q.jpg</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/c8tyaon.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fc8tyaon.jpg&d=fMmZVRBh8JxXvfCabRklGVQmTevdAkBFS5MHro4yyYg%3D&h=cf37c075\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://i.imgur.com/c8tyaon.jpg</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=w8lAowK3_58\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dw8lAowK3_58&d=fMmZVRBh8JxXvfCabRklGVQmTevdAkBFS5MHro4yyYg%3D&h=a92b6da7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=w8lAowK3_58</a><br />\n<br />\nDota2 / War3 地圖<br />\n自訂地圖 守城 溜冰 次次玩都笑到收唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我地之前無CAP開圖，後補 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n各色各類既RPG <br />\n如果你有咩想玩既 都可以係GP到找人一齊玩<br />\n我地都好樂意買GAME一齊玩 因為本身大部份人係上班族 所以有一定既經濟能力<br />\n唔洗怕要買GAME就無人陪你玩<br />\n<br />\n太多GAME 不能盡錄<br />\n試到有新既GAME好玩 會再分享比大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"2e41808091daaabdd161bceaaba686222f1075fb","tid":2404689,"uid":145108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T01:14:42.000Z","msg":"新年快樂"},{"pid":"47f529ccc2f7d67e7614176e39735fd1c70df387","tid":2404689,"uid":281557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T01:21:54.000Z","msg":"Happy New Year!!"},{"pid":"26cf71f05bed8349b860b11127b8470f9ad5ca06","tid":2404689,"uid":25602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T01:28:28.000Z","msg":"push！！！！"},{"pid":"1827bec25eae1e1b6530e9cf760cb81e82efd8c7","tid":2404689,"uid":67836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T02:42:15.000Z","msg":"小試一下囉"},{"pid":"4268c551e82189e824ff385f0e82a2768c44dd96","tid":2404689,"uid":67836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T03:13:03.000Z",